About Us
With a casual vibe, A menu which features local seasonal ingredients. The Urban Oak turns casual dining into a traditional night out with a whole new experience we call southern hospitality. Our team combined with the local fresh flavors craft to create dishes that make it difficult to forget where fun meets food. We offer indoor and a small outdoor seating and a visible kitchen that puts our guest in the center of the action. Our restaurant makes you feel at home.  The Urban Oak is a place to meet up with old friends and create new ones and is the perfect spot to savor  brews, delectable plates, and unforgettable conversation with family and friends. Welcome Home!
